# Controlled Cookie signature list for the Phase 6 protocol/decode harness
# (tests/run-protocol-tests.sh). NOT a production list. Drives the cookie half
# of module.c: ngx_http_heavybag_sig_cookie_lookup (module.c:887) walks EVERY
# "Cookie" request header (the generic ngx_list walk, not the version-coupled
# headers_in.cookie slot) and matches each value AS A WHOLE against the row --
# there is NO ;/= pair-walk, the entire header value is the subject.
#
#   sqlmap        -> 404   (bare substring: matches anywhere in the whole value)
#   ^evilcookie$  -> 403   (anchored: matches ONLY if the WHOLE value is exactly
#                          "evilcookie" -- proves no pair-walk, since "a=evilcookie"
#                          as a whole value cannot satisfy ^...$)
sqlmap         404
^evilcookie$   403
